The paper discusses the potential use of deep neural networks for cognitive robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper specifically mentions the use of deep neural networks for audio and vision data, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the limitations of deep neural networks and the need for alternative approaches, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
